snippet.title: The Hundredth Hike - Official Game Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The Hundredth Hike is an Indie Psychological Horror game, living the story of you, as a mountain hiker, reliving your tragic past and finding the calm of the nature under your boots. Unaware of what lies before you, you unleash a powerful and mysterious truth.

DEMO AVAILABLE NOW!
Demo Now Available on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3286890/The_Hundredth_Hike_Halloween_Demo/

DISCORD - https://dsc.gg/liberationgamesofficial

STEAM - https://store.steampowered.com/app/3286860/The_Hundredth_Hike/
